---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>扬德尔实验室 | Yandel Lab</title>
    <meta name="description" content="扬德尔实验室，记录技术、AI 与个人项目的长期实验。" />
    <style>
      :root {
        font-family:
          Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
          "Segoe UI", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        color: #e5e7eb;
        background: #0f172a;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25), transparent 32rem),
          radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.18), transparent 30rem),
          #0f172a;
      }

      main {
        width: min(1080px, calc(100% - 32px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 72px 0;
      }

      nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 96px;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 24px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      a {
        color: #cbd5e1;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover {
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .hero {
        max-width: 760px;
      }

      .badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.25);
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: #93c5fd;
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
        margin-bottom: 28px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(44px, 8vw, 84px);
        line-height: 1.05;
        letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      }

      .highlight {
        color: #60a5fa;
      }

      .desc {
        margin-top: 28px;
        max-width: 680px;
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.9;
        color: #cbd5e1;
      }

      .actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-top: 36px;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 44px;
        padding: 0 20px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .primary {
        color: #0f172a;
        background: #e5e7eb;
      }

      .secondary {
        color: #e5e7eb;
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
      }

      .cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 18px;
        margin-top: 96px;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 24px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
        border-radius: 24px;
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      }

      .card h2 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #94a3b8;
        line-height: 1.8;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      footer {
        margin-top: 96px;
        color: #64748b;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 760px) {
        nav {
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 18px;
          flex-direction: column;
          margin-bottom: 72px;
        }

        .cards {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          margin-top: 72px;
        }

        main {
          padding: 40px 0;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <nav>
        <div class="logo">Yandel Lab</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="/">首页</a>
          <a href="#projects">项目</a>
          <a href="#notes">笔记</a>
          <a href="#about">关于</a>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <section class="hero">
        <div class="badge">🚀 扬德尔实验室 · Yandel Lab</div>

        <h1>
          记录技术、AI 与<br />
          <span class="highlight">个人项目</span>的长期实验
        </h1>

        <p class="desc">
          这里是 Yandel 的个人主页。以后会放一些技术笔记、项目展示、AI 工具、
          开发踩坑记录，以及正在构建中的个人作品。
        </p>

        <div class="actions">
          <a class="button primary" href="#projects">查看项目</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="#notes">阅读笔记</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cards" id="projects">
        <article class="card">
          <h2>项目展示</h2>
          <p>记录正在开发或已经完成的个人项目，包括 Web 应用、后端服务和 AI 工具。</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card" id="notes">
          <h2>技术笔记</h2>
          <p>整理 Java、前端、服务器部署、Docker、Nginx、云服务等实践经验。</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card" id="about">
          <h2>关于我</h2>
          <p>一个持续学习和折腾技术的开发者，正在把想法慢慢做成真实可访问的作品。</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <footer>
        © 2026 Yandel Lab · yandel.top
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>